WEBVTT

01:40.509 --> 01:45.930
[Speed and Love]

01:46.289 --> 01:48.740
[Episode 29]

03:03.520 --> 03:04.930
What are you thinking about?

03:04.930 --> 03:05.890
Can't sleep?

03:11.800 --> 03:13.330
Why can't you sleep either?

03:13.960 --> 03:16.560
On the way here,
didn't you say you were sleepy?

03:19.840 --> 03:21.040
I can't sleep either.

03:30.329 --> 03:32.730
I didn't expect you'd prepare all this.

03:37.640 --> 03:38.930
If I don't prepare,

03:40.079 --> 03:41.450
how can I marry you?

03:43.079 --> 03:44.010
Tomorrow,

03:45.240 --> 03:47.050
I'll have a good talk with Mom.

03:55.170 --> 03:55.960
It's okay.

03:57.240 --> 03:58.050
At least

03:59.079 --> 04:00.680
she hasn't kicked me out yet,

04:01.120 --> 04:02.920
which is already good progress.

04:12.960 --> 04:14.610
Why are you in someone else's room

04:14.610 --> 04:17.209
in the middle of the night
instead of sleeping?

04:18.880 --> 04:19.630
Go back now.

05:13.910 --> 05:16.040
That thing during the day got delayed,

05:17.240 --> 05:18.500
so it wasn't finished.

05:20.530 --> 05:22.320
So I want to get it done

05:22.680 --> 05:23.810
before going to bed.

05:24.360 --> 05:25.120
Otherwise,

05:25.560 --> 05:28.160
tomorrow would bring more things
to deal with.

05:30.560 --> 05:32.490
Do you still remember how to fix it?

05:34.590 --> 05:35.500
I think I do.

05:37.300 --> 05:37.850
You do it.

05:48.760 --> 05:49.970
That's just how I am.

05:50.560 --> 05:52.409
When daytime tasks

05:52.880 --> 05:54.000
aren't done,

05:54.530 --> 05:56.260
I can't even sleep peacefully.

05:58.530 --> 06:00.590
But Jin Qiang doesn't think this way.

06:01.890 --> 06:03.280
To him, doing it today,

06:03.980 --> 06:04.930
tomorrow,

06:05.650 --> 06:06.730
or days later

06:07.120 --> 06:08.440
makes no difference.

06:10.560 --> 06:11.320
I remember

06:11.490 --> 06:13.820
he had terrible procrastination issues.

06:14.610 --> 06:15.490
Once

06:15.850 --> 06:17.910
the window screens at home got dirty,

06:18.440 --> 06:20.770
I asked him
to take them down and wash them.

06:21.680 --> 06:22.610
He actually took

06:23.240 --> 06:25.570
over a week before finally doing it.

06:28.130 --> 06:30.220
Little things like that

06:31.290 --> 06:33.320
kept us arguing nonstop.

06:36.880 --> 06:38.170
I remember back then,

06:38.970 --> 06:40.800
in our old place in Nanjing,

06:41.440 --> 06:43.360
I loved growing plants.

06:44.880 --> 06:46.210
The apartment was small

06:46.530 --> 06:47.930
and already cluttered.

06:48.710 --> 06:49.670
But Jin Qiang

06:50.240 --> 06:52.800
thought they were pointless

06:54.760 --> 06:56.420
and wouldn't let me keep them.

06:58.140 --> 07:00.090
He even smashed them.

07:03.120 --> 07:04.090
Jin Qiang, don't!

07:04.090 --> 07:05.560
-Love to keep them, huh?
-No!

07:05.560 --> 07:07.000
The house is so small,

07:07.360 --> 07:10.360
and you're cluttering it with
all this useless stuff!

07:45.170 --> 07:46.290
Remember:

07:47.409 --> 07:49.409
as a man, you should be responsible.

07:49.760 --> 07:52.220
When faced with problems and difficulties,

07:52.490 --> 07:53.760
you need to solve them,

07:54.220 --> 07:55.690
not avoid or run away

07:56.170 --> 07:57.170
from them,

07:58.680 --> 08:01.340
because that's the ultimate sign
of cowardice.

08:03.240 --> 08:04.000
Got it.

08:15.650 --> 08:16.650
Back then,

08:16.970 --> 08:18.490
we were drawn together

08:19.480 --> 08:20.830
by each other's shine.

08:23.120 --> 08:25.120
But after we actually got together,

08:25.910 --> 08:28.140
all those life's trivial problems

08:28.510 --> 08:30.240
turned everything into a mess.

08:30.970 --> 08:32.960
In endless arguments,

08:34.289 --> 08:35.720
we slowly used up

08:36.559 --> 08:38.159
what little love we had left.

09:11.410 --> 09:12.500
Do you blame me?

09:25.230 --> 09:26.380
I remember

09:28.530 --> 09:29.960
you once told me

09:32.200 --> 09:34.200
that when pruning this kind of tree,

09:36.080 --> 09:39.010
you should cut
some of the really dense leaves inside

09:39.480 --> 09:41.480
to keep the branches airy.

09:44.410 --> 09:45.470
That way the leaves

09:47.390 --> 09:49.250
won't yellow or wither so easily.

09:59.010 --> 09:59.720
Mu

10:00.410 --> 10:02.810
has been spoiled by me
since she was little.

10:03.960 --> 10:04.930
In the future,

10:05.370 --> 10:07.630
don't let her have her way in everything.

10:07.880 --> 10:08.640
Otherwise,

10:09.440 --> 10:10.730
you'll suffer for it.

10:14.770 --> 10:15.440
It's fine.

10:16.650 --> 10:18.250
I'll just keep spoiling her.

10:22.050 --> 10:23.110
Here, give it to me.

10:29.820 --> 10:30.550
Are you cold?

10:35.270 --> 10:35.960
No, I'm not.

11:20.440 --> 11:20.970
Careful.

11:21.360 --> 11:21.910
That one.

11:22.370 --> 11:23.300
This one, right?

11:25.650 --> 11:26.280
Be careful.

11:26.280 --> 11:26.850
Okay.

11:28.480 --> 11:30.240
Here, try this one.

11:32.110 --> 11:33.190
Here, hang it here.

11:33.960 --> 11:34.560
Yes.

11:36.960 --> 11:37.840
It's crooked.

11:38.680 --> 11:40.140
See? Isn't this prettier?

11:40.870 --> 11:41.350
Right?

11:42.050 --> 11:42.980
This one is good.

12:19.080 --> 12:19.750
Zhao.

12:24.800 --> 12:26.400
What were you talking about?

12:29.600 --> 12:30.600
Really?

12:31.770 --> 12:32.730
Really nothing.

12:43.560 --> 12:44.690
Are you still upset?

12:45.600 --> 12:46.320
No, I'm not.

12:47.600 --> 12:48.410
Well...

12:49.230 --> 12:50.910
do you want to back out?

12:53.350 --> 12:54.070
Never.

12:56.580 --> 13:02.980
♪ Perhaps the weather's damp and mild ♪

12:58.280 --> 12:59.160
Well...

13:00.290 --> 13:02.550
do you have anything
you want to say to me?

13:03.000 --> 13:06.830
♪ Perhaps it's about the habit
of bearing ♪

13:07.540 --> 13:10.830
♪ A certain bitter emotion ♪

13:10.850 --> 13:16.920
♪ For you, it's all too easy ♪

13:17.870 --> 13:23.580
♪ To be happy or heartbroken,
as transparent as I can be ♪

13:24.570 --> 13:30.480
♪ Crossing the line for love,
I've walked 10,000 kilometers ♪

13:24.680 --> 13:25.560
Happy New Year,

13:26.040 --> 13:26.710
Mu.

13:31.820 --> 13:37.980
♪ Brave enough to be sure is my instinct ♪

13:38.130 --> 13:39.290
♪ I believe ♪

13:39.310 --> 13:43.480
♪ Maybe it just takes a little resolve ♪

13:43.740 --> 13:46.970
♪ To turn wishes into shooting stars ♪

13:47.550 --> 13:52.580
♪ Mirroring the eyes that gaze at me ♪

13:55.370 --> 13:58.170
The Chinese New Year
has brought the house to life.

13:58.560 --> 14:01.290
This is Zhao's first time
stepping into this home

14:01.310 --> 14:04.110
and the liveliest New Year
we've had in years.

14:05.050 --> 14:06.360
Chris's other children

14:06.360 --> 14:12.180
♪ The crash of waves comes and goes ♪

14:06.440 --> 14:08.770
have all come back from different places.

14:09.370 --> 14:12.480
We put up the Fu characters
and Spring Festival couplets together.

14:12.480 --> 14:14.410
Jin Zhao's good handwriting came in handy.

14:13.200 --> 14:16.680
♪ After leaning on you and hesitating ♪

14:14.770 --> 14:16.230
The whole family is happy.

14:16.900 --> 14:20.180
♪ I've never been so steadfast and true ♪

14:16.980 --> 14:19.250
Of course, the happiest thing

14:19.770 --> 14:21.320
is that my mom,
who I've always worried about,

14:20.340 --> 14:26.180
♪ My love needs to stay clear-eyed ♪

14:21.480 --> 14:23.010
has also blended in with us.

14:27.230 --> 14:33.180
♪ After the scorching ache,
I still reach for a sincere heart ♪

14:34.530 --> 14:40.430
♪ Crossing the line for love,
I've walked 10,000 kilometers ♪

14:41.790 --> 14:47.930
♪ Brave enough to be sure is my instinct ♪

14:47.950 --> 14:53.060
♪ I believe
maybe it just takes a little resolve ♪

14:53.340 --> 14:56.680
♪ To turn wishes into shooting stars ♪

14:57.290 --> 15:01.680
♪ Mirroring the eyes that gaze at me ♪

14:58.890 --> 15:00.690
I'm especially happy this year.

15:00.890 --> 15:02.490
We're all gathered together

15:02.800 --> 15:04.600
and we have several new members.

15:05.200 --> 15:07.060
I hope that every year from now on,

15:07.320 --> 15:09.170
on this important day,

15:08.390 --> 15:15.210
♪ Crossing the path,
stepping into your life ♪

15:09.480 --> 15:11.290
we can all gather together,

15:11.440 --> 15:12.410
be happy,

15:12.770 --> 15:14.080
united as one family,

15:14.560 --> 15:16.360
and celebrate Chinese New Year.

15:17.170 --> 15:18.600
Let's raise our glasses together.

15:18.600 --> 15:20.130
-Happy New Year.
-Happy New Year.

15:20.130 --> 15:23.480
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

15:26.440 --> 15:28.800
I spent the whole afternoon
making these dishes,

15:28.800 --> 15:30.480
so you must finish them all.

15:30.650 --> 15:32.310
Here, have some soup first.

15:32.360 --> 15:34.290
Have some more of my homemade soup.

15:35.410 --> 15:36.270
Thank you, Mom.

15:36.490 --> 15:38.010
The second bowl is for Sophia.

15:38.010 --> 15:39.760
Yes. Beautiful.

15:39.840 --> 15:40.680
Thank you.

15:42.010 --> 15:42.650
Here.

15:44.410 --> 15:47.370
Chinese New Year isn't complete
without dumplings.

15:50.040 --> 15:50.970
Happy New Year.

15:51.370 --> 15:53.570
You must eat dumplings for the New Year.

15:58.320 --> 15:58.870
Here.

17:26.220 --> 17:27.349
Wait for me a moment.

17:46.170 --> 17:46.850
This—

17:47.850 --> 17:49.000
Take it back.

17:51.440 --> 17:52.640
Since you were young,

17:52.850 --> 17:55.450
you've never had elders around
to support you,

17:55.910 --> 17:58.640
so you've had to rely on yourself
for everything,

17:59.180 --> 18:00.780
and that's a lot of pressure.

18:12.750 --> 18:13.460
Auntie,

18:14.820 --> 18:15.780
I can handle it.

18:18.390 --> 18:20.250
This is just a small token from me.

18:29.610 --> 18:31.610
You're still as stubborn as you were

18:32.280 --> 18:33.480
when you were little.

18:35.510 --> 18:36.310
Alright then.

18:36.680 --> 18:38.050
I'll keep it for you.

18:54.650 --> 18:55.330
Jin Zhao.

18:55.850 --> 18:56.520
Uncle.

18:58.570 --> 19:01.370
Yinghan asked me to give this to you.

19:06.610 --> 19:07.330
This is...

19:07.650 --> 19:08.720
She didn't say what it was,

19:08.720 --> 19:10.380
just asked me to pass it to you.

19:11.880 --> 19:12.670
Take it.

19:14.820 --> 19:15.750
Alright, Uncle.

19:15.830 --> 19:16.980
Mom, we're leaving.

19:19.170 --> 19:21.760
When you get back, work hard,

19:22.330 --> 19:24.680
sleep well, eat properly,

19:25.200 --> 19:26.930
and take good care of yourself.

19:29.130 --> 19:31.500
Let me know once you land safely.

20:03.480 --> 20:05.680
Remember to take good care of yourself.

20:07.200 --> 20:08.930
So that you can take care of her.

20:15.710 --> 20:16.670
Don't forget

20:17.280 --> 20:18.610
what you promised me.

20:28.520 --> 20:29.130
Come.

20:35.640 --> 20:36.530
You two

20:36.890 --> 20:37.890
must both be well.

20:40.340 --> 20:41.250
Thank you, Mom.

20:58.760 --> 21:00.040
It's about time.

21:02.250 --> 21:02.960
Go now.

21:29.610 --> 21:30.410
Mom, look.

21:30.780 --> 21:31.980
Is my drawing pretty?

21:32.500 --> 21:34.630
So pretty, so cute.

21:35.050 --> 21:36.410
But it's still not as cute and pretty

21:36.410 --> 21:37.270
as my daughter.

21:37.850 --> 21:38.780
It's wonderful.

21:40.000 --> 21:41.720
Mom, what are you doing?

21:42.090 --> 21:44.200
I just knitted you a scarf.

21:44.410 --> 21:45.680
It's winter now.

21:45.710 --> 21:48.390
Your neck can't get cold,

21:48.610 --> 21:50.520
so I made you a scarf.

21:51.030 --> 21:52.590
That's nice. Go play now.

21:53.930 --> 21:55.340
Zhao, you're back.

21:56.440 --> 21:58.720
Look, Mom knitted me a new scarf.

21:58.890 --> 21:59.620
Is it pretty?

22:00.280 --> 22:01.000
Yes.

22:01.490 --> 22:03.550
I'm going to play with my friends now.

22:08.030 --> 22:08.830
Jin Zhao,

22:09.610 --> 22:10.280
come here.

22:19.460 --> 22:20.350
Are you cold?

22:25.860 --> 22:26.620
Are you cold?

22:38.660 --> 22:39.790
Go do your homework.

22:54.810 --> 22:57.090
Although he's not my biological child,

22:57.830 --> 22:59.790
I raised him with my own hands.

23:00.840 --> 23:02.390
Looking back now,

23:03.020 --> 23:04.150
I realize that back then

23:04.150 --> 23:06.270
I projected my resentment toward Jin Qiang

23:06.270 --> 23:08.380
onto that little kid,

23:09.810 --> 23:11.130
making him bear

23:11.130 --> 23:13.990
a lot of negative emotions
he never should have had.

23:15.930 --> 23:17.130
As time passed

23:17.650 --> 23:19.300
and I reexamined myself,

23:21.000 --> 23:24.000
I realized
he must have had some expectations of me.

23:26.520 --> 23:28.480
Those days we can never return to

23:29.500 --> 23:31.070
remain a regret.

24:00.010 --> 24:01.600
Wait here for me. I'll go get us coffee.

24:01.600 --> 24:02.160
Okay.

24:44.750 --> 24:46.660
Mu is in your hands now.

24:47.180 --> 24:48.380
Take good care of her,

24:49.150 --> 24:50.560
and yourself too.

24:52.700 --> 24:54.030
This scarf

24:54.770 --> 24:56.880
made you wait for 18 years.

24:59.110 --> 25:00.310
Don't blame Mom.

25:31.720 --> 25:32.850
The coffee's here.

25:50.280 --> 25:52.680
What's wrong? Is something bothering you?

26:01.710 --> 26:02.680
Last time I noticed

26:02.680 --> 26:05.610
your "yearning day and night" keychain
was worn out,

26:05.830 --> 26:07.630
so I thought I'd get you a new one.

26:07.780 --> 26:08.500
Where is it?

26:10.240 --> 26:11.170
Close your eyes.

26:20.180 --> 26:21.840
Why are you being mysterious?

26:22.210 --> 26:23.410
Can I open my eyes now?

26:28.340 --> 26:30.490
[Yearning Day and Night]

26:41.880 --> 26:42.990
When we were kids,

26:45.570 --> 26:46.900
we didn't get to choose.

26:48.200 --> 26:49.200
We were family,

26:51.170 --> 26:52.440
but we were torn apart.

26:55.170 --> 26:55.960
But now,

26:59.380 --> 27:01.980
are you willing
to build a family with me again?

27:23.380 --> 27:24.300
But...

27:23.470 --> 27:28.290
♪ Forgotten between the rearview mirror ♪

27:25.040 --> 27:27.330
we've only been together for a few months.

27:27.330 --> 27:29.330
Isn't this moving too fast?

27:30.620 --> 27:36.000
♪ Seeing your long unseen face
on that rainy night ♪

27:33.610 --> 27:35.330
Your math on time is a bit off.

27:36.720 --> 27:38.330
You were 20 when you got together with me,

27:38.330 --> 27:43.810
♪ Counting backwards to
the unfulfilled promises ♪

27:38.570 --> 27:39.440
and now

27:41.090 --> 27:42.090
it's been 8 years.

27:45.340 --> 27:51.000
♪ The heart that is still beating
hasn't said goodbye yet ♪

27:51.930 --> 27:54.780
♪ Meeting again after many years ♪

27:55.270 --> 27:58.180
♪ The coffee is too sour and bitter;
I'm greedy for something sweet ♪

27:59.320 --> 28:01.950
♪ Who will circle around the line
bordering the thoughts? ♪

28:02.310 --> 28:06.440
♪ Stupidly,
I refuse to believe there's an end ♪

28:07.210 --> 28:09.200
♪ I must ♪

28:09.220 --> 28:13.040
♪ Continue to love,
between the sun and the moon ♪

28:10.000 --> 28:12.090
My New Year's wish is

28:12.370 --> 28:14.040
that the person in my heart

28:13.060 --> 28:16.470
♪ Even in pain,
we indulge in the iron-like vows ♪

28:14.280 --> 28:15.850
can understand my songs,

28:16.160 --> 28:17.760
understand my feelings,

28:16.680 --> 28:18.200
♪ Willingly ♪

28:18.170 --> 28:19.810
and keep me in his heart

28:20.000 --> 28:21.960
as his moon for a lifetime!

28:20.820 --> 28:24.040
♪ At this moment ♪

28:24.260 --> 28:27.700
♪ I run towards you
before the night falls ♪

28:27.720 --> 28:32.240
♪ Don't ask about the past;
just bet on tomorrow ♪

28:32.280 --> 28:35.450
♪ Those dreams and longings ♪

28:36.960 --> 28:39.550
♪ Look at what the vast world wants ♪

28:39.570 --> 28:43.770
♪ It's nothing but a fairytale ♪

28:44.310 --> 28:47.560
♪ It's always the broken up couple ♪

28:48.010 --> 28:51.330
♪ Who reunite amidst love, hate,
and separation ♪

28:48.570 --> 28:49.480
Or...

28:50.760 --> 28:52.130
do you need a little more time to...

28:51.450 --> 28:53.440
♪ I must ♪

28:53.690 --> 28:56.870
♪ Continue to love,
between the sun and the moon ♪

28:55.720 --> 28:56.570
I'm willing.

28:57.040 --> 28:59.000
I've been waiting
for these words for so long.

28:57.060 --> 29:00.470
♪ Even in pain,
we indulge in the iron-like vows ♪

29:00.620 --> 29:02.140
♪ Willingly ♪

29:04.820 --> 29:08.040
♪ At this moment ♪

29:08.260 --> 29:11.700
♪ I run towards you
before the night falls ♪

29:11.720 --> 29:16.240
♪ Don't ask about the past;
just bet on tomorrow ♪

29:16.260 --> 29:19.430
♪ Those dreams and longings ♪

29:19.690 --> 29:23.960
♪ The trails overlap again ♪

29:37.000 --> 29:38.170
Here, take a look.

29:38.330 --> 29:41.260
This is the restaurant
for our bachelor party today.

29:41.330 --> 29:42.480
You're so impatient. Come on.

29:42.480 --> 29:43.170
Red hair.

29:43.720 --> 29:44.850
Tomorrow is my good buddy

29:44.850 --> 29:46.570
Brandy's wedding day.

29:46.590 --> 29:47.170
Crazy.

29:48.330 --> 29:49.960
You've gained weight.
You've got a double chin.

29:49.960 --> 29:50.960
Come on, Brandy!

29:52.190 --> 29:53.450
Can you stop chatting?

29:54.200 --> 29:56.060
Save the sweet talk for tomorrow.

29:56.200 --> 29:59.000
Focus on the bachelor party
for your bro, will you?

29:59.650 --> 30:00.440
So lame.

30:03.010 --> 30:04.540
Jiang Mu!

30:05.200 --> 30:06.040
Come on.

30:06.480 --> 30:07.720
Stop chatting with Brandy.

30:07.720 --> 30:09.330
Let us have him for the bachelor party.

30:09.330 --> 30:10.410
I'm not texting him.

30:10.410 --> 30:12.810
I'm just confirming tomorrow's schedule.

30:12.930 --> 30:14.240
Brandy only smiles that happily

30:14.240 --> 30:15.640
when he's talking to you.

30:17.330 --> 30:18.190
I'll go ask him.

30:18.240 --> 30:19.200
Come on, Brandy!

30:20.300 --> 30:22.700
-Let's go.
-Are you chatting with Jiang Mu?

30:23.330 --> 30:25.010
Always drinking. Come on.

30:27.170 --> 30:28.330
Don't cross the line.

30:28.330 --> 30:29.660
You're not married yet.

30:29.660 --> 30:31.720
You have to wait until after tonight.

30:32.060 --> 30:33.450
Sit down.

30:33.480 --> 30:35.890
-You're really meddling too much.
-They should sit together.

30:35.890 --> 30:37.000
You got dragged down.

30:37.000 --> 30:38.200
A gentleman doesn't fight with a woman.

30:38.200 --> 30:40.130
Together. It's more fun that way.

30:42.130 --> 30:44.240
Are you groomsmen capable of it?

30:44.370 --> 30:46.330
Don't mess up the wedding tomorrow.

30:46.330 --> 30:48.340
Who are you saying isn't capable?

30:48.370 --> 30:50.090
That sounds so unpleasant.

30:50.240 --> 30:51.170
Crazy and I

30:51.550 --> 30:52.620
have prepared

30:53.000 --> 30:55.410
two new suits.

30:55.850 --> 30:57.760
Tomorrow at the wedding,

30:58.170 --> 30:59.570
we're going to dazzle...

31:01.110 --> 31:02.420
you all.

31:10.280 --> 31:11.170
Jiang Mu!

31:11.570 --> 31:12.760
We're here!

31:15.000 --> 31:16.130
Keep bragging.

31:16.350 --> 31:18.440
Just make sure you answer the questions,

31:18.440 --> 31:19.520
or you won't even get through the door.

31:19.520 --> 31:21.720
Come on, how hard can your questions be?

31:21.760 --> 31:23.420
How hard can our questions be?

31:23.720 --> 31:25.810
We have plenty of hard questions.

31:25.930 --> 31:28.930
Our questions are about traditions
of the Chinese...

31:31.520 --> 31:32.650
Stop asking.

31:33.210 --> 31:34.750
You'll see tomorrow.

31:35.520 --> 31:37.380
Don't make things too hard for us.

31:37.720 --> 31:40.050
Don't you want your friend to get married?

31:41.250 --> 31:42.380
That's impossible.

31:42.440 --> 31:43.720
Let me give you a tip.

31:44.040 --> 31:44.890
You guys

31:45.240 --> 31:47.480
can make up for your lack of brains
with red envelopes,

31:47.480 --> 31:50.040
so you won't fail to win the bride.

31:50.440 --> 31:52.300
Red envelopes make up for brains?

31:52.780 --> 31:54.580
Our brains are more than enough.

31:55.130 --> 31:56.000
Right, Brandy?

31:57.680 --> 32:00.440
You can mess with us

32:00.760 --> 32:02.020
all you want tomorrow,

32:02.230 --> 32:04.470
but my brother Brandy

32:05.780 --> 32:07.060
has to marry Jiang Mu.

32:08.280 --> 32:09.340
Am I a real brother?

32:10.690 --> 32:12.570
So tomorrow you're getting married.

32:12.570 --> 32:13.480
Bride,

32:13.730 --> 32:14.590
how do you feel?

32:15.130 --> 32:16.200
Honestly,

32:16.940 --> 32:18.660
I don't really know how I feel.

32:19.040 --> 32:19.900
You don't know?

32:20.020 --> 32:21.330
I thought you'd say something

32:21.330 --> 32:22.960
like nervous or excited.

32:23.240 --> 32:24.040
Yeah.

32:24.320 --> 32:25.560
People say

32:26.090 --> 32:27.760
marriage is a milestone,

32:27.890 --> 32:29.620
where you say goodbye to youth.

32:29.810 --> 32:31.000
But for me,

32:31.330 --> 32:33.440
the ones I love are all by my side,

32:33.680 --> 32:34.650
and my youth

32:35.040 --> 32:36.390
is right here with me.

32:40.650 --> 32:42.200
Don't worry, everyone.

32:42.360 --> 32:44.480
I've already done a lot of divinations.

32:44.480 --> 32:46.960
Tomorrow's wedding will be perfect.

32:49.040 --> 32:50.540
You don't believe me?
I can do it again right now.

32:50.540 --> 32:51.650
No need to do it.

32:51.930 --> 32:53.190
I'm already set on him.

32:55.590 --> 32:57.350
Then let me interview Brandy.

32:58.090 --> 32:59.330
Are you nervous?

32:59.520 --> 33:00.920
That's a silly question.

33:01.170 --> 33:01.930
Well,

33:02.170 --> 33:03.440
he's a boxer

33:03.440 --> 33:04.720
and a racer.

33:05.090 --> 33:06.760
The whole world could be nervous,

33:06.760 --> 33:07.960
but he won't be.

33:08.440 --> 33:09.520
The only variable

33:09.810 --> 33:10.650
is you

33:10.760 --> 33:12.320
fainting at the wedding.

33:14.550 --> 33:15.200
Brandy,

33:15.540 --> 33:16.410
nervous?

33:20.520 --> 33:21.280
A little.

33:24.570 --> 33:25.570
I wish you two

33:25.980 --> 33:27.140
a marriage

33:27.930 --> 33:29.060
that lasts forever.

33:29.300 --> 33:30.030
Absolutely!

33:30.320 --> 33:32.250
Tomorrow, leave the wedding to us.

33:32.330 --> 33:33.680
It'll definitely be a success!

33:33.680 --> 33:34.330
Cheers!

33:34.760 --> 33:35.330
Come on!

33:35.480 --> 33:36.860
Come on! Bottoms up.

33:36.890 --> 33:38.150
-Bottoms up!
-Cheers!

34:35.770 --> 34:36.600
Time to get up.

34:40.880 --> 34:41.469
Pan Kai.

34:41.980 --> 34:42.840
Keep drinking!

34:45.790 --> 34:46.650
Liang Yanfeng?

34:47.000 --> 34:48.360
Drink with us...

34:48.960 --> 34:49.810
What?

34:51.100 --> 34:51.710
Crazy.

34:52.420 --> 34:53.020
Crazy?

34:54.699 --> 34:55.340
Lin Sui!

35:10.990 --> 35:11.680
Sanlai!

35:15.930 --> 35:17.190
Let me sleep a bit more.

35:21.150 --> 35:22.870
Time to get up.

35:33.600 --> 35:34.300
Sister!

35:34.330 --> 35:36.290
Wake up! It's the wedding day.

35:36.730 --> 35:37.890
What?

35:39.290 --> 35:41.000
Hello, hello. Wake up.

35:41.000 --> 35:42.690
I'm getting married.

35:43.480 --> 35:46.330
Nana! Stop sleeping, Nana.

35:47.370 --> 35:48.530
Nana! Nana!

35:48.560 --> 35:49.820
I can't drink anymore!

35:51.560 --> 35:52.290
What should we do?

35:52.290 --> 35:54.470
My bridesmaids don't seem able to attend.

35:54.470 --> 35:55.160
Mine too.

35:57.290 --> 35:59.090
Just the two of us will be enough.

36:03.770 --> 36:04.520
Let's elope.

36:23.760 --> 36:25.090
Where are you two going?

36:25.310 --> 36:26.190
Come back!

36:27.010 --> 36:28.080
-It was your fault for drinking that much!
-Brandy!

36:28.080 --> 36:29.040
You're not getting married?

36:28.560 --> 36:31.010
♪ It all began the moment I met you ♪

36:29.250 --> 36:31.210
-Where are you going?
-We're going to get married by ourselves.

36:31.030 --> 36:33.500
♪ There's a pull I cannot explain ♪

36:31.560 --> 36:32.760
Where are they going?

36:32.850 --> 36:34.040
I don't know. What does this mean?

36:33.530 --> 36:36.650
♪ My eyes follow you,
my heart chases after you ♪

36:36.450 --> 36:37.370
In the past, I was

36:36.670 --> 36:38.480
♪ I just can't help it ♪

36:38.020 --> 36:39.100
fearless about everything.

36:38.500 --> 36:40.950
♪ When I gaze across the sky ♪

36:40.130 --> 36:41.250
But now I'm not anymore,

36:40.980 --> 36:43.480
♪ Not even miles can keep us apart ♪

36:42.080 --> 36:43.040
because I know

36:43.500 --> 36:46.510
♪ Sweet longing drifts on the wind ♪

36:43.600 --> 36:44.860
you're waiting for me.

36:46.040 --> 36:47.520
I don't want to be your weakness.

36:46.530 --> 36:48.750
♪ I can feel you near ♪

36:48.210 --> 36:49.690
I am your navigator.

36:48.770 --> 36:51.200
♪ Feel you're with me ♪

36:50.690 --> 36:51.850
I thought my life

36:51.220 --> 36:53.520
♪ Forget the sunsets, forget the tides ♪

36:52.440 --> 36:53.700
would have no more surprises,

36:53.700 --> 36:55.760
♪ Watch the years pass
and wander the world ♪

36:54.000 --> 36:55.330
but luckily, I have you.

36:56.040 --> 36:57.890
So, Mr. Jin Zhao,

36:56.110 --> 36:57.790
♪ You're the only one in my heart ♪

36:57.810 --> 37:00.480
♪ It all began the moment I met you ♪

36:58.370 --> 37:00.730
are you willing to spend
the rest of your life with Ms. Jiang Mu?

37:00.510 --> 37:02.640
♪ The road ahead ♪

37:01.770 --> 37:02.560
I am.

37:02.900 --> 37:04.900
♪ And every step we take ♪

37:04.920 --> 37:07.540
♪ Guide us toward happiness ♪

37:05.780 --> 37:09.530
He used to set out and return alone.

37:10.410 --> 37:13.820
♪ We'll both be there ♪

37:10.480 --> 37:11.370
From now on,

37:11.890 --> 37:13.290
we will set out together.

37:14.330 --> 37:15.660
And our destination...

37:16.300 --> 37:17.110
is home.

37:20.590 --> 37:23.170
[The End]
